SliTaz Mirror Tools
===============================================================================


This package provides tools for a SliTaz mirror such as helper scripts.
These tools are used on our official SliTaz mirror and should help other
mirror admins to get a custom mirror with SliTaz branding, backup, etc.

****
Move dvd and floppies to slitaz-forge/dvd and slitaz-forge/floppies since
ther are virtual full hosts.
****

The configuration files used on mirror.slitaz.org are in the slitaz-forge
repository.


===============================================================================
